('668e68f6-07d8-4484-8819-bad42635e44f', 'Streamlined Automation of Membership Renewal Campaigns Through Salesforce Integration', 'streamlined-automation-of-membership-renewal-campaigns-through-salesforce-integration', 'The client is a U.S.-based provider of business coaching and learning solutions. They specialize in delivering coaching programs and educational resources designed to improve leadership skills, drive organizational growth, and facilitate professional development. ', '{\"testimonials\":{\"points\":[{\"content\":\"The app was launched on AppExchange and received widespread acclaim. The team at Cynoteck Technology Solutions Pvt. Ltd excelled at project management, with them regularly complying with all deadlines and communicating all issues in advance\",\"authorName\":\"Peter Connel \",\"authorTitle\":\"CEO, CallPro CRM \",\"image\":null}]},\"impact\":{\"points\":[{\"heading\":\"Achieved a cost-effective solution\",\"description\":\"by leveraging Salesforce features, eliminating the need for external tools.\"},{\"heading\":\"The fully automated solution\",\"description\":\"reduced campaign execution efforts by approximately 80%. \"},{\"heading\":\"Automated response \",\"description\":\"logging and notifications significantly improved turnaround times.\"}]},\"overview\":{\"description\":\"The client is a U.S.-based provider of business coaching and learning solutions. They specialize in delivering coaching programs and educational resources designed to improve leadership skills, drive organizational growth, and facilitate professional development. \"},\"challenge\":{\"points\":[\"The client ran several membership renewal campaigns each year, aimed at distinct customer segments. \",\"Their campaign workflow involved disconnected tools: Form Assembly for forms, Mailchimp for emails, and Salesforce as the CRM. \",\"The lack of system integration created inefficiencies and manual work across all campaign stages. \",\"The client needed an automated, streamli